### ============================================================
### US-ROOM-01 / US-ROOM-02 / US-ROOM-03 — Room create, list, view,
### update, and bulk create (Landlord only; nested under a property).
### ============================================================
### Run in the "local" (or "device") environment from
### rest-client.env.json. The login block below captures
### @accessToken / @refreshToken for every request that follows.
### ============================================================
### ============================================================
# @name login
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "{{email}}",
  "password": "{{password}}"
}

### capture tokens
@accessToken = {{login.response.body.data.accessToken}}
@refreshToken = {{login.response.body.data.refreshToken}}

### ------------------------------------------------------------
### Resolve a property to attach rooms to (reuse existing or create)
### ------------------------------------------------------------
# @name createProperty
POST {{baseUrl}}/properties
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Rooms Test Property",
  "address": "1 Room St, District 1, HCMC"
}

###
@propertyId = {{createProperty.response.body.data.id}}

###

### ============================================================
### INTENDED TO SUCCEED
### ============================================================

### US-ROOM-01 — Create a single room
### Expect 201 { data:{ id, name, baseRent, propertyId, ... } }
# @name createRoom 
POST {{baseUrl}}/properties/{{propertyId}}/rooms
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Room A",
  "baseRent": 3000000
}

###
@roomId = {{createRoom.response.body.data.id}}

###

### US-ROOM-03 — Bulk create rooms (auto-numbering friendly)
### Expect 201; every row created atomically.
POST {{baseUrl}}/properties/{{propertyId}}/rooms/bulk
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "rooms": [
    { "name": "Room B", "baseRent": 3200000 },
    { "name": "Room C", "baseRent": 3400000 }
  ]
}

###

### US-ROOM-02 — List rooms for the property
### Expect 200 paginated; Room A/B/C appear.
GET {{baseUrl}}/properties/{{propertyId}}/rooms
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

###

### US-ROOM-02 — View a single room
### Expect 200 { data:{ id, name, baseRent, ... } }
GET {{baseUrl}}/rooms/{{roomId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

###

### US-ROOM-02 — Update room details (name + baseRent)
### Expect 200 with updated values. Occupancy/status cannot be set.
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/rooms/{{roomId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Room A (Renamed)",
  "baseRent": 3100000
}

###

### ============================================================
### INTENDED TO FAIL
### ============================================================

### Create room with missing name (expect 400 VALIDATION_ERROR)
POST {{baseUrl}}/properties/{{propertyId}}/rooms
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "baseRent": 3000000
}

###

### Create room with negative baseRent (expect 400 VALIDATION_ERROR)
POST {{baseUrl}}/properties/{{propertyId}}/rooms
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Room Bad",
  "baseRent": -100
}

###

### Attempt to set occupancy/status (expect 400 — not an accepted field)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/rooms/{{roomId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "Occupied"
}

###

### Bulk with empty rooms array (expect 400 VALIDATION_ERROR)
POST {{baseUrl}}/properties/{{propertyId}}/rooms/bulk
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "rooms": []
}

###

### Create room on a property owned by another landlord (expect 404)
POST {{baseUrl}}/properties/{{otherLandlordPropertyId}}/rooms
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Room X",
  "baseRent": 1000000
}

###

### Unauthenticated room list (expect 401 UNAUTHENTICATED)
GET {{baseUrl}}/properties/{{propertyId}}/rooms

###
